        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/mike_zimbric/{size}/2295_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-12-08T04:53:29.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ve had two bottles of this wine and loved them.  Went back to get more.  Really lovely stuff.  This wine, their village level Puligny and the Folatieres from 2014 were hits at a dinner group \u2018meeting\u2019 about 6-8 months ago.  Their reds are nice as well.  Martin has been right on about these.</p>",
