      {
        "id": 2311922,
        "name": "N@th@n V@nd\u20acrgrift",
        "username": "Nathan_V",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/f04885/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-12-08T15:21:56.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Martin Steinley\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Martin Steinley:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thank you, gentlemen.  Alan, more information here: <a href=\"https://vintage59.com/our-portfolio/bachelet_monnot_puligny/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://vintage59.com/our-portfolio/bachelet_monnot_puligny/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Ha! They are my go to Puligny these days along with Jean-Marc Pillot for Chassagne and Fichet for Mersault. Prices for Bachelet have gone up significantly between 2012 and 2015 though\u2026</p>",
        "post_number": 7,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 11,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-03T02:01:53.349Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
